data.description: Located Minutes from Rock Spring and Chickamauga!  This Completely Remodeled Split Level sits on *5 ACRES*. Has Mountain Views from back yard and Master bedroom. Offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, living room with kitchen area. Has a Den with wood burning fireplace open kitchen and a 2 car garage. This has is practically a Brand New Home!! It has a New Roof, New HVAC, New Windows, New LVP Flooring throughout the house. New Kitchen with appliances. New bathrooms. New ceilings, New Wiring including light fixtures, New Plumbing. New Panel Box. Added landscaping .New gravel down driveway. New interior paint and trim and doors. New siding!
